WHAT ABOUT THAT GIRL?

22
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,583
THE THIRD SAPLING
FROM CORSICA?

23
00:02:57,666 --> 00:03:00,791
- I HAVE SOME FAITH IN HER.

24
00:03:09,166 --> 00:03:11,041
