26
00:03:12,958 --> 00:03:16,583
♪ WE'LL NEVER BE APART ♪

27
00:03:16,666 --> 00:03:20,625
♪ THE SUN YOU SEE IS ME... ♪

28
00:03:20,708 --> 00:03:22,916
- Mireille: NOIR,

