00:09:29,041 --> 00:09:31,375
ARE YOU LISTENING
TO ME, ALTENA?!

95
00:09:31,458 --> 00:09:35,958
ALL WE'VE WORKED FOR IS OVER
FOR YOU AND YOUR DAMN NOIR. 

96
00:09:36,041 --> 00:09:39,291
- NO, THE RITUAL
WILL STILL BE PERFORMED.

97
00:09:39,375 --> 00:09:42,916
