ENTIRELY UNEXPECTED.

98
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:45,208
BUT THERE IS STILL
ONE LAST TRIAL

99
00:09:45,291 --> 00:09:47,458
THAT MUST BE OVERCOME.

100
00:09:47,541 --> 00:09:49,666
- ALTENA?
- ALL THAT MATTERS

101
00:09:49,750 --> 00:09:51,333
IS THAT THE BLADES OF OLD

102
00:09:51,416 --> 00:09:53,625
SHALL BE BROUGHT BACK
INTO THIS WORLD.

103
00:09:53,708 --> 00:09:58,250
YES, EVEN IF IT ALREADY
BELONGS TO THE <i>SOLDATS.</i>

104
00:09:58,333 --> 00:10:01,500
- ARE YOU SAYING
THAT YOU DON'T EVEN CARE

105
00:10:01,583 --> 00:10:04,000
WHAT HAPPENS TO THE <i>SOLDATS</i>
 BECAUSE OF NOIR?

106
00:10:04,083 --> 00:10:06,458
- "THE MAN WITHIN THE MAN.

107
00:10:06,541 --> 00:10:08,666
THE LOVE WITHIN THE LOVE.

108
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,458
THE SIN WITHIN THE SIN."

109
00:10:10,541 --> 00:10:15,000
THE <i>SOLDATS</i> WERE CREATED 
TO ADDRESS CERTAIN TRUTHS

110
00:10:15,083 --> 00:10:17,625
THAT EXIST WITHIN
THE SOCIETY OF MAN.

111
00:10:20,708 --> 00:10:22,875
BUT IN THE LONG YEARS SINCE,

112
00:10:22,958 --> 00:10:25,208
THE <i>SOLDATS</i> LOST THEIR WAY.

113
00:10:25,291 --> 00:10:29,916
NOW, RAVAGED BY THE VERY DISEASE
THEY SOUGHT TO CONTAIN,

114
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:33,041
THEY WRITHE LIKE MAGGOTS
IN SOCIETY'S FLESH.

115
00:10:33,125 --> 00:10:36,666
- YOU CAN'T MEAN--
- TO REMOVE THAT FLESH,

116
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,666
WE NEED A PURE
UNTAINTED BLADE,

117
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:40,791
A BLADE DEVOID OF BINDINGS,

118
00:10:40,875 --> 00:10:42,916
FREE TO CUT WITH
THE WILL OF GOD.

119
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:48,375
AND ONCE NOIR
HAS BEEN REVIVED,

120
00:10:48,458 --> 00:10:51,708
THAT IS WHEN THE IDEALS
OF THE <i>SOLDATS</i> OF OLD, 

121
00:10:51,791 --> 00:10:54,333
"THE GRAND <i>RETOUR"</i> THAT
WE HAVE WAITED FOR

122
00:10:54,416 --> 00:10:56,208
WILL BE REALIZED AT LAST.

123
00:10:56,291 --> 00:10:59,208
- YOU'VE INTENDED FOR THIS
TO HAPPEN ALL ALONG.

124
00:11:02,541 --> 00:11:03,625
( grunts )

125
00:11:17,125 --> 00:11:19,000
- THE TWO OF YOU ARE THE ONES

126
00:11:19,083 --> 00:11:20,791
WHO WILL OVERCOME
THE FINAL TRIAL. 

127
00:11:20,875 --> 00:11:22,916
THE BOND YOU SHARE

128
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,791
IS THE MARK
OF THE TRUE NOIR.

129
00:11:25,875 --> 00:11:29,166
WELCOME, NOIR.
I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU.

130
00:11:29,250 --> 00:11:32,250
- SO YOU'RE ALTENA, HUH?

131
00:11:32,333 --> 00:11:35,958
OR PERHAPS I SHOULD SAY,
"SO WE MEET AT LAST."

132
00:11:36,041 --> 00:11:38,166
- THIS ISN'T
OUR FIRST MEETING, CHILD.

133
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:39,458
IN TRUTH,
I HAVE LONG

134
00:11:39,541 --> 00:11:41,958
WATCHED OVER ALL OF YOU
FROM THE SHADOWS,

135
00:11:42,041 --> 00:11:45,083
EVEN YOU,
MY DAUGHTER OF CORSICA.

136
00:11:45,166 --> 00:11:46,458
- DON'T YOU DARE
CALL ME THAT!

137
00:11:57,833 --> 00:12:01,250
- Altena: THIS IS YOUR LAST,
MOST DANGEROUS TRIAL.

138
00:12:01,333 --> 00:12:03,500
COME, CHILDREN.

139
00:12:04,958 --> 00:12:07,666
LET THE RITUAL NOW BEGIN.

140
00:12:18,125 --> 00:12:21,041
- THE SURFACE WORLD
IS FULL OF SUFFERING,

141
00:12:21,125 --> 00:12:24,000
BUT NOIR IS ALWAYS THERE
IN THE DARK,

142
00:12:24,083 --> 00:12:26,875
FIGHTING TO PROTECT
THE GRIEVING CHILDREN.

143
00:12:29,083 --> 00:12:32,333
THIS IS THE TRUE FORM 
OF THE <i>SOLDATS</i> OF OLD,

144
00:12:32,416 --> 00:12:35,916
TWO MAIDENS WHO FORGE
A PERFECT BALANCE.

145
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,625
- ( distant gunfire )

146
00:12:38,708 --> 00:12:43,333
- ( girl shrieks in distance )

147
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:48,125
- ( people scream in distance )

148
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:33,208
- Altena:
IF LOVE CAN KILL PEOPLE,

149
00:13:33,291 --> 00:13:37,541
THEN SURELY HATRED
CAN SAVE THEM.

150
00:14:00,708 --> 00:14:02,958
- ( child cries )

