152
00:14:34,541 --> 00:14:37,583
THE TRUE RITUAL
WILL BE STAGED.

153
00:14:41,458 --> 00:14:45,541
IT IS A PLACE LOST
IN THE EDDIES OF TIME.

154
00:14:45,625 --> 00:14:47,375
AND IN THIS
FORGOTTEN PLACE,

155
00:14:47,458 --> 00:14:50,375
YOUR PILGRIMAGE
WILL COME TO AN END.

156
00:14:50,458 --> 00:14:53,125
- SO MANY PEOPLE HAVE DIED,

157
00:14:53,208 --> 00:14:55,833
INNOCENTS AND <i>SOLDATS,</i>

158
00:14:55,916 --> 00:14:59,875
MIREILLE'S FAMILY,
AND NOW CHLOE TOO.

159
00:14:59,958 --> 00:15:02,875
WHAT PURPOSE
DID IT SERVE?!

160
00:15:02,958 --> 00:15:04,500
- ( chuckles )

161
00:15:04,583 --> 00:15:06,875
FOOLISH CHILD.

162
00:15:06,958 --> 00:15:08,833
SO FOOLISH, BOTH OF YOU.

163
00:15:08,916 --> 00:15:11,916
YOUR MOTHER WAS
A FOOL LIKE THAT AS WELL.

164
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:14,166
- ( gasps )
- YOUR PARENTS WERE BOTH FOOLS

165
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:16,333
WHO LET AFFECTION
FOR THEIR PROGENY

166
00:15:16,416 --> 00:15:18,416
BLIND THEM TO THE SIGHT
OF THE TRUTH.

167
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:20,708
BUT THEY DID
SERVE QUITE WELL

168
00:15:20,791 --> 00:15:23,916
AS LAMBS TO BE SACRIFICED
UPON YOUR ALTER.

169
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,916
- ( gasps )

170
00:15:28,083 --> 00:15:29,375
( grunts )

171
00:15:32,333 --> 00:15:33,833
HOW DARE YOU,
YOU MONSTER! 

172
00:15:37,833 --> 00:15:39,916
- HMM.

173
00:16:08,166 --> 00:16:10,833
- YOU'RE NOT WORTH IT!

174
00:16:10,916 --> 00:16:14,458
IT'S NOT WORTH SOILING
A BULLET TO KILL YOU. 

175
00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:16,500
- ISN'T IT?

176
00:16:16,583 --> 00:16:18,875
THAN I HAVE NO CHOICE.

177
00:16:18,958 --> 00:16:19,916
- ( screams )

178
00:16:21,291 --> 00:16:22,750
( winces )

179
00:16:27,166 --> 00:16:30,250
- GO AHEAD, CHILD.
IF YOU DO NOT SHOOT,

180
00:16:30,333 --> 00:16:32,208
THEN YOUR FRIEND
WILL SURELY DIE.

181
00:16:32,291 --> 00:16:35,666
- ( gasps )
- YES, SO MANY LIVES

182
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:37,416
HAVE ALREADY BEEN TAKEN.

183
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,875
SO MANY BY YOUR HANDS.

184
00:16:39,958 --> 00:16:41,791
ARE YOU REALLY
GOING TO LET

185
00:16:41,875 --> 00:16:44,416
ALL THOSE LIVES 
GO TO WASTE NOW?

186
00:16:48,291 --> 00:16:51,000
SURELY, YOU OUGHT TO KNOW IT
AS WELL AS I.

187
00:16:51,083 --> 00:16:53,666
YOU ARE NOIR, MY CHILD--

188
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:56,083
BORN UNDER
THE MARK OF CAIN,

189
00:16:56,166 --> 00:16:58,250
RAISED IN A CRADLE OF SIN,

190
00:16:58,333 --> 00:17:01,166
A SUPREME PRESENCE 
THAT GOVERNS DEATH.

191
00:17:01,250 --> 00:17:04,750
IT IS THE PURPOSE
FOR WHICH YOU EXIST,

192
00:17:04,833 --> 00:17:07,333
YOUR SOLE REASON
FOR BEING.

193
00:17:07,416 --> 00:17:11,000
- THAT CAN'T--

194
00:17:11,083 --> 00:17:12,458
IT CAN'T BE!

195
00:17:12,541 --> 00:17:16,708
- Altena: YOU HAVE COMMITTED
SIN UPON SIN AS NOIR.

196
00:17:16,791 --> 00:17:20,958
AND THOSE SINS WILL EXIST
FOR ALL ETERNITY.

197
00:17:23,375 --> 00:17:25,083
( chuckles )

198
00:17:25,166 --> 00:17:28,583
YOU NEEDN'T BE
SADDENED BY THIS

199
00:17:28,666 --> 00:17:30,791
FOR THOSE SINS ARE NECESSARY

200
00:17:30,875 --> 00:17:34,125
AS LONG AS THE WORLD
OF MAN EXISTS.

201
00:17:34,208 --> 00:17:38,541
YOU ARE ONE WHO HAS BEEN
SELECTED FOR THAT PURPOSE.

202
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:41,375
NOW, PULL THE TRIGGER,
CHOSEN ONE.

203
00:17:41,458 --> 00:17:43,958
KILL ME FOR ALL MY SINS

204
00:17:44,041 --> 00:17:46,291
AND LIVE ON
AS A TRUE NOIR.

205
00:17:46,375 --> 00:17:48,375
- ( breathing heavily )

206
00:17:52,083 --> 00:17:53,250
( gasps )

207
00:18:03,958 --> 00:18:06,500
- PLEASE GUARD MY MIREILLE.

208
00:18:06,583 --> 00:18:08,375
- HUH?

209
00:18:11,125 --> 00:18:12,208
- ( gasps )

210
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:18,083
- ( gasps )

211
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:24,625
- KIRIKA!

212
00:18:27,083 --> 00:18:30,000
- ( groaning )

213
00:18:30,083 --> 00:18:32,333
( gasps sharply )

214
00:18:40,083 --> 00:18:42,083
( strains )

215
00:18:42,166 --> 00:18:46,250
OUR HANDS
MAY INDEED BE BLACK.

216
00:18:46,333 --> 00:18:47,875
( inhales slowly )

217
00:18:47,958 --> 00:18:52,500
AND PERHAPS THOSE SINS...
( breathes raggedly )

218
00:18:52,583 --> 00:18:54,583
WILL NEVER VANISH.

219
00:18:54,666 --> 00:18:55,916
( moans )

220
00:18:56,000 --> 00:19:01,500
BUT MY SINS
ARE YUMURA KIRIKA'S

221
00:19:01,583 --> 00:19:02,958
AND NOT NOIR'S

222
00:19:03,041 --> 00:19:07,916
BECAUSE WE ARE NOT
WHAT YOU THINK WE ARE.

223
00:19:10,291 --> 00:19:11,291
- ( gasps )

224
00:19:14,250 --> 00:19:15,875
KIRIKA!

225
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:24,625
KIRIKA!

226
00:19:24,708 --> 00:19:27,458
- <i>SAYONARA,</i> MIREILLE.

227
00:19:35,958 --> 00:19:37,041
- KIRIKA!

228
00:19:40,916 --> 00:19:43,208
( strains )

229
00:19:46,833 --> 00:19:48,791
- LET GO, MIREILLE.

230
00:19:48,875 --> 00:19:50,666
LET GO.

231
00:19:52,333 --> 00:19:54,583
- ( Mireille cries )

232
00:19:58,375 --> 00:20:00,625
KIRIKA.

233
00:20:00,708 --> 00:20:02,833
I'M BEGGING YOU.

234
00:20:02,916 --> 00:20:05,625
( cries )

235
00:20:10,166 --> 00:20:12,166
PLEASE.

236
00:20:53,625 --> 00:20:56,250
- IT'S NOIR.

237
00:20:56,333 --> 00:20:58,166
- NOIR'S JUST A NAME.

238
00:20:58,250 --> 00:21:00,125
- BUT YOU'LL STAND ASIDE

239
00:21:00,208 --> 00:21:02,375
IF YOU FEAR
THE HEART OF DARKNESS.

240
00:21:17,541 --> 00:21:20,333
- SO, WHAT DO YOU
INTEND TO DO NOW?

241
00:21:20,416 --> 00:21:23,708
YOU MUST KNOW THAT THIS
IS BY NO MEANS THE END.

242
00:21:23,791 --> 00:21:26,791
- WHO CAN PREDICT
THE FUTURE?

243
00:21:26,875 --> 00:21:29,833
